		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm having fun making reproductions and I'm looking for a good hex editor.  I  am currently using  XVI32 and it sucks.  It's especially difficult to double my file so that I can put a small rom on a larger eprom (I can't find how I can paste after the last bit???  I can only paste inbetween the 2nd to last and last..  What kind of crap is that?). 
<br />
<br />Since many of you have already shopped around for the best hex editor, would you share your expertise please?

		

		</td>
